  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Kinetite</em></p>\n<p>A 5-foot diameter sphere of compressed lightning appears in an unoccupied space of your choice and lasts for the duration. Each creature within 5 feet of the sphere when the power is cast must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes [[/r 5d8]] lightning damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one. </p>\n<p>As a bonus action on each of your turns, you can move the ball of lightning up to 30 feet vertically or horizontally. If you ram the sphere into a creature, that creature must make a Dexterity saving throw or take [[/r 5d8]] kinetic damage (or half as much damage on a success), and the sphere stops moving this turn. A creature takes half as damage on a successful Dexterity saving throw.</p>\n<p><strong><em>Force Potency.</em></strong> When you cast this power with a force slot of 6th level or higher, both the lightning and kinetic damage increase by [[/r 1d8]] for each slot level above 5th.</p>",
